TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on slba_facility to retrieve the item_id where SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE = '--' and SLBA_FACILITY.DIVISION_GROUP = 'sld'
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_FACILITY1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MAX(SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_ID) as FACILITY_ID, SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE as FACILITY_CODE, SLBA_FACILITY.DIVISION_GROUP as DIVISION_GROUP FROM SLBA_FACILITY WHERE SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE = '--' AND SLBA_FACILITY.DIVISION_GROUP = 'sld' GROUP BY SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE, SLBA_FACILITY.DIVISION_GROUP

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: LKP_DAY_DIMENSION transformation performs a lookup on target table, DAY_DIMENSION
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_DAY_DIMENSION1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT min(DAY_DIMENSION.AS_OF_DATE) AS AS_OF_DATE, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_YEAR_YYYY AS CY_YEAR_YYYY, min(DAY_DIMENSION.CY_MONTH_NUM) AS CY_MONTH_NUM, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_YEAR_YYYY||LPAD(DAY_DIMENSION.CY_WK_OF_YEAR,2,'0') AS CY_WK_OF_YEAR, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_YEAR_YYYY||LPAD(DAY_DIMENSION.CY_WK_OF_YEAR,2,'0') AS FISCAL_YR_WK_ID FROM DAY_DIMENSION GROUP BY DAY_DIMENSION.AS_OF_DATE, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_YEAR_YYYY, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_YEAR_YYYY||LPAD(DAY_DIMENSION.CY_WK_OF_YEAR,2,'0')

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: SQ_TSUM_C11 transformer reads data from tables, 1)TLU_STYLE 2)TSUM_C11 3)TLU_CUR_WK
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_TSUM_C11

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT C.SKU_ID, SUBSTR(C.EVENT_ID,3,2), C.FYR_WK_ID, S.ITEMS_PER_PACK, C.ACTL_CNCL_DOL_AMT, C.ACTL_CNCL_COS_AMT, C.ACTL_CNCL_UNIT_QTY,C.EVENT_ID, TRIM(S.STYLE_ID) FROM PCATWH.TSUM_C11 C, PCATWH.TLU_SKU K, PCATWH.TLU_STYLE S WHERE C.SKU_ID=K.SKU_ID AND K.STYLE_ID=S.STYLE_ID AND C.FYR_WK_ID=(SELECT FYR_WK_ID FROM PCATWH.TLU_CUR_WK) AND (C.ACTL_CNCL_UNIT_QTY > 0 OR C.ACTL_CNCL_DOL_AMT > 0 OR C.ACTL_CNCL_COS_AMT > 0) AND SUBSTR(C.EVENT_ID,3,2) NOT IN('71','72')
